---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
import ThoughtsList from "../../components/ThoughtsList.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Thoughts · Monishver Chandrasekaran"
  description="Ruminations and realizations as I walk through my journey of life."
>
  <section class="head">
    <h1>Thoughts</h1>
    <p class="sub">Ruminations and realizations, penned as they arrive</p>
    <hr class="flourish" />
  </section>
  <p class="intro">
    These notions are ruminations and realizations as I walk through my
    journey of life. Some are mine; some belong to others and resonated
    deeply enough to keep. Everyone sees life through their unique lens, and
    this is my way of sharing what mine has caught. If you have thoughts that
    are raw, genuine, and come from a place that doesn't intend harm &mdash;
    express them.
  </p>
  <ThoughtsList mine={true} />
</Base>

<style>
  .head {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 3rem;
  }
  .head h1 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin: 0 0 0.35rem;
  }
  .sub {
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin: 0;
  }
  .flourish {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    width: 5rem;
    margin: 1.6rem auto 2rem;
  }
  .intro {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
  }
</style>
